SUMMARY:Mother’s Day Brunch
DESCRIPTION:Celebrate Mother’s Day at Hard Truth Distilling Co. with a relaxed, open‑seating brunch experience in the House of Rye. Gather with family and friends and enjoy the rustic charm, wooded surroundings, and signature Hard Truth hospitality that make events here unforgettable.\nPair your meal with handcrafted cocktails or sips from the mimosa bar, then enjoy a stroll through the distillery grounds as you continue your Mother’s Day celebration.\nMenu announcement coming soon.\nHandcrafted cocktails and mimosa bar will be available for additional purchase.\nBuffet is all ages; must be 21+ to purchase and consume alcohol.\nSeating is limited, so make your reservation today.\n
