SUMMARY:Rumble On The Rocks | Night 1
DESCRIPTION:ROUND 1: RUMBLE ON THE ROCKS \nIt’s on. The bands are locked in, the stage is set, and Round 1 of Rumble on the Rocks is bringing serious heat.\nCome out and experience a full night of live music as these bands battle it out for a shot at the finals—and a chance to win BIG:\n\n$2,500 + a performance at Amplify Nashville$1,500 + a performance at Amplify Nashville\n\nNIGHT ONE FEATURES:\n\nSlow Gin\nBuck Knawe & The Quick Draw\nZillafyde\nSweet Pea & The Pods\nHigh Street Jack\nWest Fork Revival**Order of performance is determined on the day of the event and may not match the above order**\n\nThis is a FAN-VOTED competition; your vote decides who moves on.\n\n\nVoting details:\nBallots are $10\nEach ballot = votes for TWO bands\nTop TWO bands advance to the finals\n\nExpect fast-paced sets, quick transitions, and nonstop energy from start to finish.\n\nPro tip: Come early, stay loud, and support your favorite bands—crowd turnout makes a difference.\nThis isn’t just a show… it’s a showdown.\n
URL:https://browncounty.com/?post_type=mec-events&p=297709
ORGANIZER;CN=Hard Truth Distilling Co.:MAILTO:events@bwqoht.com
CATEGORIES:Entertainment,Food &amp; Drink,Free,Live Music,Outdoor Concerts,Special Events,Summer
LOCATION:418 Old State Rd 46, Nashville, IN 47448
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/png:https://browncounty.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/05/RumbleOnTheRocks-1080.png
END:VEVENT
