SUMMARY:Rumble On The Rocks | Round 1 Night 2
DESCRIPTION:ROUND 1 CONTINUES: RUMBLE ON THE ROCKS\nNight two is here—and a whole new lineup of bands is ready to take the stage and bring everything they’ve got.\nIf you missed night one, this is your chance. If you were there, you already know… this competition is no joke.\nThese bands are battling for a spot in the finals—and a shot at:$2,500 + a performance at Amplify Nashville$1,500 + a performance at Amplify Nashville\n\nNIGHT TWO FEATURES:\n\nHoney White\nBengebreakers\nKnollwood Kings\nSustayn\n46 Drifters\nSarah Barton and 2nd That**Order of performance is selected on the day of the event, and is not reflected by the listing above**\n\nThis is a FAN-VOTED competition. You decide who moves on.\n\nVoting details:Ballots are $10Each ballot = votes for TWO bandsThe top two bands from the night advance to the finals\n\nExpect another night of high-energy, fast-paced sets and nonstop music.\nBring your crew, show up loud, and back your favorite bands—every vote counts.\nNew night. New bands. Same stakes.\n
