SUMMARY:11th Annual Hilly Half | 10K | 5K
DESCRIPTION:The Brown County YMCA Hilly Half Marathon highlights our county, promote health, well-being and create a true sense of community. The Half Marathon scenic route starts and finishes at the Saddle Barn/Lower Shelter house winding its way through picturesque Brown County State Park. Up hills, past the fire tower, vistas and then a fast 2 mile downhill finish\n
