SUMMARY:Touch-A-Truck
DESCRIPTION:The Brown County Touch-A-Truck event is a FREE, hands-on event that provides kids with the opportunity to see, touch and explore their favorite big trucks, heavy equipment and emergency vehicles as well as interact with community support leaders including police officers, firemen, construction workers and more! Bring the entire family to get up close with these vehicles, learn about what they do, how they work and how they benefit our community!\nFor more information, go to https://www.browncountytouchatruck.com/\n
