SUMMARY:Chippendales (21+) – Talk Dirty To Me World Tour
DESCRIPTION:For audiences 21+\nGrab your squad and break away from your every day for a night with Chippendales as the 2026 “Talk Dirty To Me” World Tour makes a stop at the Brown County Music Center in Nashville, Ind., on Friday, June 12, 2026 (for audiences 21+).Chippendales is the premier destination for a thrilling and unforgettable night out! The world-famous male revue show has been entertaining audiences for over 45 years, continually raising the bar with each performance. Celebrated as a 14-time Best of Las Vegas Gold Award winner for Best Male Revue Show, the production brings its iconic blend of entertainment and sensuality to audiences around the globe. But Chippendales is more than just a show – it’s an experience. Whether you’re celebrating a special occasion or just looking for a fun night out with friends, this show is the perfect way to let loose and have fun! With stunning stage design, high-energy music, and interactive elements that get the audience involved, you’ll feel like you’re part of the action.\n
