DESCRIPTION:We would like to invite you to the 13th GPGT that started in 2011!\nA very limited amount of discounted tickets are available now, as well as Early Arrival (Thursday) Tickets, Saturday Only Tickets, and Primitive RV/Camper/Bus Parking Passes.​\nCome celebrate an amazing weekend with us in the beautiful hills of Brown County!\n2 Days and Nights of Live Music, Live Art, Light Shows, Camping, Workshops, Kids Activities, Running Water Restrooms, Showers($5), and much more!!!\nKids 12 and under are free!There will be free face painting during the day and a kids parade on the Saturday of the event.For more info:Hover over the “Home” tab and then click “Festival Info” as well as clicking the “More Info” tab of this page.We can’t wait to see you!!!\n​\n
