SUMMARY:Mother’s Day Candle Pouring Experience
DESCRIPTION:Celebrate your favorite kind of “mom” – whether that’s your human mom, your dog mom friend, your cat mom sister… or yourself \nThis cozy, creative evening is all about making something thoughtful, personal, and just a little bit adorable.\n\n What you’ll make:A custom-scented candle poured into a limited-edition keepsake mug, paired with the cutest cozy socks for a ready-to-gift (or keep for yourself ) moment.\n\n Choose your mug: “I love that you’re my mom” “In a perfect world, every home would have a dog and every dog would have a home” “In a perfect world, every home would have a cat and every cat would have a home”Each mug comes with coordinating cozy socks…because candles + comfort = perfection.\n\n Your experience includes: Guided candle pouring Custom scent blending from our fragrance library Your choice of mug + socks A relaxed, feel-good atmosphere (perfect for catching up, laughing, and slowing down a bit)\n\n A note about timing:Candles require time to cool (approximately 2–3 hours). Candles from pouring experiences that start at 5:30pm will be ready for pick up after 11am the next day; candles from pouring experiences that start at 10am will be ready for pick up after 2pm that same day.\n\n Perfect for:• Treating your mom• Celebrating a dog or cat mom in your life• A girls’ night/morning out• Making something meaningful for yourself\n\n Pricing:Early Bird: $45 (first six seats)Standard: $48\nSpots are limited (and these mugs are too) so grab your seat early! \n
URL:https://browncounty.com/events/mothers-day-candle-pouring-experience/
ORGANIZER;CN=Lakehouse Candle Company:MAILTO:mandy@browncountycrafts.com
