DESCRIPTION:Pickin’ in the Backwoods Music Festival, presented by The Coyote Radio Show and Podcast and Duke’s Indy, is an event you won’t want to miss! Immerse yourself in the scenic backwoods of Brown County, Indiana, for an unforgettable two-and-a-half-day experience like no other.\nCrafted with real music fans in mind, this festival is all about fostering a close-knit atmosphere. With tickets highly limited, attendees are guaranteed an exceptionally intimate live show.\n-BYOB – Campfire Jams – Dance Lessons – Camping – Free Parking – Vendors – Food Trucks-\nWe want this festival to be interactive so BRING A INSTRUMENT TO JAM AROUND THE CAMPS AT NIGHT!\n
