SUMMARY:Blueprints + Breakthroughs
DESCRIPTION:Every bold idea starts with a blueprint—a vision sketched in the margins, mapped on whiteboards, or imagined in moments of quiet curiosity. But blueprints alone don’t change the world. It takes courage, experimentation, and perseverance to turn those plans into breakthroughs. At TEDxBrownCountySchools 2025, we explore the intersection of design and disruption, planning and action, imagination and impact. This year’s theme—Blueprints & Breakthroughs—celebrates the thinkers, builders, and changemakers who turn rough drafts into revolutions.\n\nWhether it’s a student reimagining education, an innovator challenging rural norms, or a quiet voice with a bold solution, our stage will showcase the sketches that became sparks—and the sparks that became something bigger. Join us as we celebrate ideas worth building—and ideas worth breaking through.\n\n
URL:https://browncounty.com/events/blueprints-breakthroughs/
CATEGORIES:Classes &amp; Workshops,Family Friendly,Happening,Special Events
LOCATION:200 Maple Leaf Boulevard, Nashville, IN 47448
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://browncounty.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/Music-Center.jpg
END:VEVENT
