SUMMARY:Mini Camp
DESCRIPTION:Grades K-2 Completed\nMini Camp is the perfect introduction to summer camp for our youngest campers! This half-week session is specially designed for children who are ready for their first overnight camp experience but may not be quite ready for a full week away from home. Packed with all the fun of camp – like swimming, crafts, songs, nature walks, and campfires – Mini Camp offers an environment where young campers can build confidence, independence, make new friends, and experience the joy of camp life.\n\n\nSessions:\n\n\n3C: June 30-July 3, 2026\n\n\n\n\nRates:\n\n\n$150 per camper\n\n\n\n\n
